      <scopecontent id="aspace_cd9a1026072530dd2f345dd47b52e6da">
         <head>Scope and Contents</head>
         <p>The materials document the production of broadsides by both individual artists and fine presses from the early to mid-20th century to the present day.</p>  
      </scopecontent>
      <arrangement id="aspace_e00b047357553980628d557e7c245b67">
         <head>Arrangement</head>
         <p>Holdings are arranged alphabetically by either artist or press name.</p>  
      </arrangement>
